        <p class="text-frost-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 text-justify">
          Primary downlink over UHF GMSK to the global SatNOGS receiver network.
          Doppler correction is bootstrapped autonomously: FFT centroid analysis
          on a received heartbeat waveforms is cross-referenced with SatNOGS receipt
          timestamps to derive orbital TLEs, which means no reliance on NORAD is required.
          A bidirectional link enables TLE uplink and command injection.
          Multi-band omnidirectional antenna (UHF/L/S) based on partial-ground-plane
          loop design, co-integrated with the CubeSat structure.
        </p>




